column2: b'One thing Ive noticed about repeat SPAC teams - the economics for us the investor, decreases while the economics for the team remains the same or better.  This is bullshit.  $LSACU IPOd as a 1 common/1 full warrant.  Acquired $VINC.  SPAC 2 $LSAQ is common only. My policy = no'
